                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.50 Recovery/2–249: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Peiping</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Clubb</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1949-02-05T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 5, 1949—5 p. m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>66. Rptd Shanghai 204, Nanking 181. ECA agrees recommendation final para Contel
                    167 Feb 2 subject Lapham’s approval. Dept concurs.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
